                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepOne" class="panel-collapse collapse in" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingOne">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>TJ-SIF2016 SECRETARIAT has already sent the invitations to both of English & computer contact persons at each PCSH Schools. <u>If you are a contact person at a PCSHS and have not got the invitation yet, please ask TJ-SIF2016 SECRETARIAT for it immediately.</u></p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
