                            </h4>
                        </div>
                        <div id="stepTwo" class="panel-collapse collapse" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="headingTwo">
                            <div class="panel-body">
                                <p>The contact persons in PCSHS <strong>MUST</strong> register first.</p>
                                <p>When register your information, choose account type:</p>
                                <ul class="list-unstyled">
                                    <li>A. The English contact person is a <mark>“Contact person”</mark>.</li>
                                    <li>B. The computer contact person who…
                                        <ul>
                                            <li>B-1. takes care of student projects is a <mark>“Participant”</mark>.</li>
                                            <li>B-2. doesn’t take care of student projects is a <mark>“Contact person”</mark>.</li>
                                        </ul>
                                    </li>
                                </ul>
                                <table class="table table-bordered table-hover table-condensed">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th></th>
                                            <th class="text-center">The kind of CP</th>
                                            <th class="text-center">Students project</th>
                                            <th class="text-center">Account type</th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr class="danger">
                                            <td class="text-center">A</td>
                                            <td class="text-center">English</td>
                                            <td class="text-center">-</td>
                                            <td class="text-center">"Contact person"</td>
